WEBVTT

00:00.898 --> 00:02.636
<i>Previously on</i> Damages...

00:02.831 --> 00:04.636
Dean Gulickson from the
<i>Times</i> called again.

00:04.758 --> 00:06.949
Thanks for agreeing
to talk to me about the case.

00:07.051 --> 00:09.884
I can give you all of
it if you do something for me.

00:09.990 --> 00:13.513
There's a High Star employee
over there-- Christopher Sanchez--

00:13.643 --> 00:16.942
and he's missing, or he's been killed.
I want you to find him.

00:17.057 --> 00:20.112
My options with you
are very limited, Chris.

00:20.206 --> 00:22.512
You betrayed me!
You talked to lawyers!

00:25.256 --> 00:28.515
Go ahead and laugh, because it's
the last thing you will ever do.

00:28.822 --> 00:30.706
His name is Gerald Boorman.

00:30.810 --> 00:32.561
And the French
government gave you his file?

00:32.677 --> 00:36.134
We may be able to pressure him
into turning against Howard Erickson.

00:36.233 --> 00:41.090
You helped Erickson cover up the
deaths of three High Star employees.

00:41.244 --> 00:42.378
We don't want you.

00:42.478 --> 00:44.916
- Well, who do you want?
- Howard Erickson.

00:45.022 --> 00:47.872
- My agency gave me time off.
- You came to see me?

00:48.032 --> 00:49.358
Jerry?

00:52.167 --> 00:53.741
You talk to Sanchez?

00:53.833 --> 00:55.340
He forced my hand.

00:57.309 --> 00:58.385
He's got to go.

